# DeepMind_Query Backend Environment Variables

# ========== API Keys ==========
# Set the API key for LLM calls. The system automatically routes based on model name:
# - MiniMax-* models use MiniMax API (https://api.minimaxi.com/anthropic)
# - claude-* models use official Anthropic API (https://api.anthropic.com)

# For MiniMax: Use your MiniMax API key
# For Anthropic: Use your Anthropic API key
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# ========== Model Support ==========
# Supported models:
# - MiniMax-M2.7 (MiniMax API)
# - claude-sonnet-4-20250514, claude-opus-4-20250514, etc. (Anthropic API)
